Package: splineClusterDetector
Type: Package
Title: Utilities for cluster detection and significance classification using splines
Version: 0.6.2
Author: Howard Burkom, Luke Mullany
Maintainer: Luke Mullany <luke.mullany@jhuapl.edu>
Description: This package provides utilities for manipulating time series of 
    location-based counts of events to detect clusters, and to determine the
    significance of these clusters via spline approach.
License: MIT + file LICENSE
Encoding: UTF-8
LazyData: true
RoxygenNote: 7.3.2
Imports: 
    cli,
    data.table (>= 1.16.0),
    geosphere,
    ggplot2,
    plotly
Depends: 
    R (>= 2.10)
Suggests: 
    Rnssp,
    sf
